title: What Is Russia's Putin Doing in Syria?
text:
What Is Putin Up To? Even after Russia's airstrikes in Syria, the Obama administration has few options. By Paul D. Shinkman Sept. 30, 2015 | 5:15 p.m. EDT
+ More What’s Russian President Vladimir Putin up to? Even with Wednesday’s sudden airstrikes , the U.S. isn’t sure.
Russia’s cagey and surreptitious moves in recent days leave the Obama administration with few options, and little idea of how far Moscow will go.
